Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.97,0:21:35.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you used that voice changer to. mimic\Nher voice and lured them to come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:38.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you used that anesthetic gun and\Na soccer ball to knock them down, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:40.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was great, Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.31,0:21:41.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can thank me for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.31,0:21:45.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had to come out of the toilet of\Na restaurant to go up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:49.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you didn't leave like\Nyou did back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:51.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,things wouldn't have gotten\Nas complicated as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.52,0:21:57.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'have no idea that'd you'd be held up\Nby a middle-agedilady'like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.70,0:22:00.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.33,0:22:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Kid's lunch's gotten cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.17,0:22:06.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. I'll be with you in a minute.
